# Built web assets are staged here by scripts/build-web.sh and embedded into
# the binary via //go:embed all:webdist. The build output is generated, so it
# is NOT tracked — except the placeholder index.html, which guarantees the
# embed directory has a real file on a fresh checkout so `go build` always
# works without first running the web build.
*
!.gitignore
!index.html
